Class FacebookRegexPatternPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fiu_CaSPR.Frank.Constants.FacebookRegexPatternPool

  • public class FacebookRegexPatternPool
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by fhu004 on 6/15/2015. This class holds all the regex patterns, as well as items that require global access. It is a singleton class that holds the accesstoken, cookies, username, and other singleton variables.
